<unclear>ἀν</unclear><supplied reason="lost">δρὶ ὡς ἡ ἡμετέρα</supplied> 

    <lb n="16"/><supplied reason="lost">ἐγ</supplied>αμήθη, <unclear>π</unclear>ροσῄει ἀ<unclear>ξι</unclear>οῦσα ὥστε <unclear>ἀ</unclear>πολαβεῖν ἢ τὰ ὑ<unclear>π</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ά</supplied><unclear>ρ</unclear>χοντα ἢ τὰ δύο <num value="2"/> τάλαντα. ἀγνωμονούσης τῆς διʼ ἐναντί<unclear>α</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ς </supplied><gap reason="lost" quantity="15" unit="character"/> 

