    <lb n="18" break="no"/>τηγίαν, δεῖ γὰρ τὰ ἀληθῆ <unclear>λ</unclear>έ<unclear>γ</unclear>ειν, <unclear>π</unclear>ροσῆλθεν κατὰ <unclear>τ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ὴ</supplied><unclear>ν</unclear> ὑπογραφὴν τῆς ἡγεμονίας τῷ ἐπιστρατήγ<unclear>ῳ</unclear>, πα<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="16" unit="character"/> 


    <lb n="19"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="2" unit="character"/>ελη ὁ Κολλοῦ<unclear>θο</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ς</supplied>. μ<supplied reason="lost">ε</supplied><unclear>τ</unclear>ὰ ταῦτα γέγονεν α<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/> τ<unclear>ῷ</unclear> ἀνδρὶ καὶ τῇ παιδί. ὅθεν μεταξὺ γεγ<supplied reason="lost">έ</supplied>νηται χρ<unclear>όν</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ος πολὺς </supplied><gap reason="lost" quantity="11" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="20"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="character"/>α<unclear>θ</unclear>εις. πάρεισιν οἱ <choice><reg>μεσῖται</reg><orig>με<unclear>σ</unclear>εῖται</orig></choice>. ἀξιοῦμεν ἢ κατ<supplied reason="lost">αγραφ</supplied>ῆναι τὸ <expan><ex>τρίτον</ex></expan> <expan><ex>δωδέκατον</ex></expan> τῶν ὑπαρχόντων ἢ τὰ δύο <num value="2"/> τάλαντ<unclear>α</unclear> <supplied reason="lost">ἀποδοθῆναι. Σαραπίων</supplied> 

